Bank Of New York Mellon Trimmed Vulcan Materials Co (VMC) Stake, Lodge Hill Capital Has Decreased Martin Marietta Matls (MLM) Stake By $3.34 Million


					
						July 25, 2017 - By Kurt Siggers

Lodge Hill Capital Llc decreased Martin Marietta Matls Inc (MLM) stake by 5.21% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Lodge Hill Capital Llc sold 15,100 shares as Martin Marietta Matls Inc (MLM)’s stock rose 4.98%. The Lodge Hill Capital Llc holds 274,900 shares with $60.90M value, down from 290,000 last quarter. Martin Marietta Matls Inc now has $14.46 billion valuation. The stock rose 0.67% or $1.53 reaching $228.53. About 354,134 shares traded. Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) has risen 23.49% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 6.79% the S&P500.







Bank Of New York Mellon Corp decreased Vulcan Materials Co (VMC) stake by 5.71% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Bank Of New York Mellon Corp sold 172,281 shares as Vulcan Materials Co (VMC)’s stock rose 5.55%. The Bank Of New York Mellon Corp holds 2.85M shares with $356.15 million value, down from 3.02 million last quarter. Vulcan Materials Co now has $16.89B valuation. The stock rose 0.77% or $0.97 reaching $127.47. About 471,057 shares traded. Vulcan Materials Company (NYSE:VMC) has risen 10.59% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has underperformed by 6.11% the S&P500.
Since February 17, 2017, it had 0 insider purchases, and 7 sales for $7.14 million activity. Shares for $334,071 were sold by McCunniff Donald A.. MCDONALD WILLIAM E also sold $1.32M worth of Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) on Friday, February 17. Nye C Howard also sold $2.45 million worth of Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) shares. PEREZ LAREE E also sold $656,952 worth of Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) on Friday, February 17. Shares for $1.55 million were sold by LLOYD ANNE H. $636,360 worth of Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) was sold by COLE SUE W. Guzzo Dana F. sold 829 shares worth $198,330.
Among 11 analysts covering Martin Marietta (NYSE:MLM), 7 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 4 Hold. Therefore 64% are positive. Martin Marietta had 16 analyst reports since August 5, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. Bank of America downgraded the shares of MLM in report on Wednesday, November 16 to “Neutral” rating. The stock of Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) earned “Buy” rating by Cleveland on Friday, March 31. The stock has “Overweight” rating by Alembic on Thursday, June 9. Goldman Sachs downgraded the shares of MLM in report on Tuesday, October 11 to “Neutral” rating. The firm has “Buy” rating given on Thursday, August 6 by Bank of America. Stifel Nicolaus maintained Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) on Wednesday, August 5 with “Buy” rating. Goldman Sachs maintained the stock with “Buy” rating in Wednesday, June 8 report. The company was upgraded on Monday, April 3 by Cleveland. The stock of Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) earned “Buy” rating by SunTrust on Wednesday, October 26. The rating was upgraded by Suntrust Robinson to “Buy” on Wednesday, October 26.
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.98 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.24, from 1.22 in 2016Q3. It worsened, as 46 investors sold MLM shares while 165 reduced holdings. 65 funds opened positions while 141 raised stakes. 60.58 million shares or 0.58% less from 60.93 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Salem Invest Counselors Inc holds 0.21% of its portfolio in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) for 8,295 shares. Mutual Of America Cap Mgmt Llc reported 0.03% in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM). State Of New Jersey Common Pension Fund D has 0.52% invested in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) for 545,000 shares. Alkeon Capital Management Ltd Liability Corporation owns 0.96% invested in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) for 220,000 shares. Aristotle Management Limited Liability holds 1.47 million shares. Hartford Invest Mngmt has 15,280 shares. Blackrock Fund stated it has 0.05% in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM). First Eagle Invest Ltd Liability Com holds 584,835 shares or 0.33% of its portfolio. Moreover, Scopus Asset Limited Partnership has 1.04% invested in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) for 210,742 shares. Sunbelt Securities holds 0% of its portfolio in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) for 889 shares. 18,018 are held by Harvey Capital Mgmt. Select Equity Grp Lp has 844,408 shares for 0% of their portfolio. Icon Advisers reported 0.62% of its portfolio in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM). Oregon Pub Employees Retirement Fund reported 13,077 shares stake. Jw Asset Mngmt Ltd Limited Liability Company holds 1.47% of its portfolio in Martin Marietta Materials, Inc. (NYSE:MLM) for 10,000 shares.
