BNY Mellon's Pershing Launches No-Transaction-Fee ETF Platform: FundVest® ETFBNY Mellon's Pershing launched its new no-transaction-fee (NTF) exchange-traded fund (ETF) platform: FundVest® ETF. The NTF platform requires no purchase minimums or holding period, and will be available to all Pershing clients.READ PRESS RELEASE











 







